To config DOpus4, you only need create/edit a new class and then enter:

Name: TrueTypeFont	ID: TTF		Match: $00010000

and, on Double-Click: AmigaDos TTFViewer {f}
(as you, for sure, know ;)


thats all,
I hope this tool can be useful for someone..
